CODE: 
PACKAGE CODE: 
package mypackage; 
 
public class Square {     private double side; 
 
    public Square(double side) {         this.side = side; 
    } 
 
    public double getSide() {         return side; 
    } 
 
    public double getArea() {         return side * side; 
    } 
 
    public double getPerimeter() {         return 4 * side; 
    } 
} 
MAIN CODE: 
import mypackage.Square; 
 
public class MainClass {     public static void main(String[] args) { 
        Square square = new Square(5.0); 
 
        System.out.println("Side of the square: " + square.getSide()); 
        System.out.println("Area of the square: " + square.getArea()); 
        System.out.println("Perimeter of the square: " + square.getPerimeter()); 
    } 
} 
